CONTROLLER.JS:  manipulates *MODEL and *VIEW.  all HTML buttons call a method in CONTROLLER
	HANDLERS:  object
		METHODS:
			DISPLAY*:
				ARGS:  1
					ID: number
						PURPOSE: to access the correct * from *MODEL
				RETURNS:  undefined
				BEHAVIOR:  retrieves the right * from *MODEL and calls the *VIEW to render that profile
			ADD*:
				ARGS: depends on profile type
					PURPOSE: passing in all required fields for a new profile 
				RETURNS:  undefined
				BEHAVIOR:  calls *MODEL to add a new profile with the new info.  calls *VIEW to redraw the home page.

